To install:

Move your the file to /Applications/nerdstream. The structure should look like:

/Applications/nerdstream/
/Applications/nerdstream/com.sierrabravo.nerdstream.agent.plist
/Applications/nerdstream/install.py
/Applications/nerdstream/isightcapture
/Applications/nerdstream/nerdstream.py
/Applications/nerdstream/uninstall.py
/Applications/nerdstream/flickrapi/
/Applications/nerdstream/flickrapi/__init__.py
/Applications/nerdstream/flickrapi/cache.py
/Applications/nerdstream/flickrapi/exceptions.py
/Applications/nerdstream/flickrapi/multipart.py
/Applications/nerdstream/flickrapi/reportinghttp.py
/Applications/nerdstream/flickrapi/tokencache.py
/Applications/nerdstream/flickrapi/xmlnode.py


Once the files are in /Applications/nerdstream, then load terminal and go to /Applications/nerdstream. Then run the install script like so:

python install.py

The install script should instruct you through the rest.